-- Richards Bay Coal Terminal Exports From South Africa  Rose 3.3% in 2011
-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 2012-01-09T12:58:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-09/richards-bay-coal-terminal-exports-from-south-africa-rose-3-3-in-2011.html
Richards Bay Coal Terminal, on  South
Africa ’s east coast, shipped 65.5 million metric tons of the
fuel in 2011, 3.3 percent more than a year earlier, according to
Bloomberg calculations based on data published on the company’s
website today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  